folder: West Farms Road & East 167th Street., Bronx, NY
original_title: Bronx: West Farms Road - East 167th Street.
text:
West Farms Road, at the south-east corner of East 167th Street, showing the Foxhurst Mansion, also known as the Tiffany House. It was built by Mr. William W. Fox in 1848 on his extensive estate. Apartment buildings were later erected on the site.

View 1: Gift of Randall Comfort 1898
View 2: E. P. Chrystie June 17, 1923
